title: Zach & Rachel: Meant to Be?
description:
Becca and Michelle are joined by Zach this week for a heartfelt conversation about his incredible date with Rachel and why he feels their connection was meant to be!  

Plus, Becca and Michelle discuss Jacob and Hayden’s controversial comments toward Gabby, and Ashley Cooke spills the tea on the one-on-one elimination that shocked us all. 

Don’t forget to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
